trans-unit.source: Contains a strongly typed collection of <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> objects.
Adds a specified <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> to this collection.
The <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> to add.
The zero-based index of the added <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref>.
Appends a set of specified permission entries to this collection.
An array of type <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> objects that contains the permission entries to add.
Appends a set of specified permission entries to this collection.
A <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntryCollection"></xref> that contains the permission entries to add.
Determines whether this collection contains a specified <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> to find.
`true` if the specified <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> belongs to this collection; otherwise, `false`.
Copies the permission entries from this collection to an array, starting at a particular index of the array.
An array of type <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> that receives this collection's permission entries.
The zero-based index at which to begin copying the permission entries.
Determines the index of a specified permission entry in this collection.
The permission entry to search for.
The zero-based index of the specified permission entry, or -1 if the permission entry was not found in the collection.
Inserts a permission entry into this collection at a specified index.
The zero-based index into the collection at which to insert the permission entry.
The permission entry to insert into this collection.
Gets or sets the object at a specified index.
The zero-based index into the collection.
The <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueuePermissionEntry"></xref> that exists at the specified index.
Performs additional custom processes after clearing the contents of the collection.
Performs additional custom processes before a new permission entry is inserted into the collection.
The zero-based index at which to insert value.
The new value of the permission entry at index.
Performs additional custom processes when removing a new permission entry from the collection.
The zero-based index at which value can be found.
The permission entry to remove from index.
Performs additional custom processes before setting a value in the collection.
The zero-based index at which oldValue can be found.
The value to replace with newValue.
The new value of the permission entry at index.
Removes a specified permission entry from this collection.
The permission entry to remove.
